OL,3,CSnowy conditions cause schools to
OL,4,Cclose and travel disruption
OL,6,FSnowy conditions described as "the
OL,7,Ffirst taste of winter" have caused
OL,8,Fschool closures, train cancellations
OL,9,Fand road delays in Wales after severe
OL,10,Fweather warnings were issued.
OL,12,FThe Met Office has issued six yellow
OL,13,Fwarnings for snow and ice with the
OL,14,Fwarning for Wales in place until 10:00
OL,15,FGMT on Wednesday, 20 November.
OL,17,FOn Tuesday, more than 160 schools are
OL,18,Fclosed across the country.
