OL,6,FIn Wrexham, 50 schools were closed,
OL,7,Fwhilst Powys saw 16 shut because of
OL,8,Fsnowy conditions.
OL,10,FFlintshire currently has 66 schools
OL,11,Fclosed and in Denbighshire 8 are
OL,12,Faffected.
OL,14,FIn Torfaen 10 schools were closed and
OL,15,FBlaenau Gwent 20 shut.
