OL,3,CSnowy conditions cause schools to
OL,4,Cclose and travel disruption
OL,6,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,7,Fhas issued the first amber cold
OL,8,Fweather health alert of the season,
OL,9,Fwarning conditions could be dangerous
OL,10,Ffor vulnerable people, including the
OL,11,Felderly.
OL,13,FNational Rail warned the cold climate
OL,14,Fwould affect various routes on
OL,15,Fnorthern train services until at least
OL,16,F2pm on Tuesday.
OL,18,FNational Highways also sent out a
OL,19,Fsevere amber weather alert for snow.
