OL,6,FDr Agostinho Sousa, from the UKHSA,
OL,7,Fsaid: "This is the first amber Cold
OL,8,FWeather Health Alert of the season,
OL,9,Fbut we can expect more as we approach
OL,10,Fwinter, and it is vital to check in on
OL,11,Fvulnerable friends, family and
OL,12,Fneighbours to ensure they are well
OL,13,Fprepared for the onset of cold
OL,14,Fweather."
OL,16,FParticularly if they are elderly or
OL,17,Fotherwise at increased risk."
OL,19,FThe Alzheimer's Society warned that
OL,20,Fcold weather can be "particularly
OL,21,Fchallenging" for people with dementia."
