OL,6,F"With high energy bills and food
OL,7,Fprices it is understandable that some
OL,8,Fmay think they have to cut back on
OL,9,Ffood and turn their heating off, but
OL,10,Fprolonged exposure to cold
OL,11,Ftemperatures can have a serious impact
OL,12,Fon an older person's health,
OL,13,Fespecially if they are already trying
OL,14,Fto manage existing illnesses," she
OL,15,Fsaid.
